Class BeliefDesire

public abstract class BeliefDesire extends Object implements IDesire
The abstract Class BeliefDesire defines a basic framework for implementing a desire which gets it's information from an agents belief.
Author:
Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (minor contribution)
